title: Robyn Carr-Sunrise Point
description: In this 19th installment of her Virgin River series, Tom Cavanaugh returns home to take over his family's apple orchard and settle down. Single mom Nora Crane is nothing like the kind of woman he thought he' d fall for- yet he can' t take his eyes off her. And while they have different concepts about family, they soon find out how quickly those ideas can change.
